			(effects
				(font
					(size 1.27 1.27)
					(thickness 0.15)
				)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "Omron G6K-2F-Y DC12 SMD DPDT latch relay, 12V coil ~1.315k. Coil pin1=K5_LATCH (+), pin8=P1/GND; primary pole COM3=K5_COM, NO4=K5_LATCH, NC2 unused; auxiliary pole COM6=GND, NO5=K6_RET, NC7 unused. Raw P4 reaches K5_LATCH through normally-closed K6; after a Türruf pulse the primary pole seals the coil from P2. The auxiliary NO contact directly gates K6's LED return, while GPIO4 senses it only through R44. D1 is the coil flyback clamp."
			(at 0 0 270)
			(unlocked yes)
			(layer "F.Fab")
			(hide yes)
			(uuid "d5e92f81-b4e4-47b4-88f6-b491e68022d7")
